10th floor of Caravelle Saigon\"><div class=\"ffb-id-4sk0mc11 fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Saigon Saigon Bar hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang m\u1edf c\u1eeda t\u1eeb th\u1ee9 Hai \u0111\u1ebfn Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt <br \/>t\u1eeb 16:00 \u0111\u1ebfn 01:00 v\u1edbi l\u1ecbch ch\u01a1i nh\u1ea1c nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\">&Acirc;m nh\u1ea1c s&ocirc;i \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">T\u1eeb 21:00 \u0111\u1ebfn khuya, Th\u1ee9 Hai \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ee9 Ba&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\">Giai \u0111i\u1ec7u Latinh<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;Ban nh\u1ea1c Living Cuba s\u1ebd l&agrave;m ch\u1ee7 s&acirc;n kh\u1ea5u v&agrave; mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng nh\u1ecbp \u0111i\u1ec7u Latin y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n t\u1eeb 21h00 \u0111\u1ebfn khuya, th\u1ee9 T\u01b0, th\u1ee9 N\u0103m, th\u1ee9 S&aacute;u, th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y v&agrave; Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt h&agrave;ng tu\u1ea7n.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\">Ladies' Night<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">M\u1ed7i th\u1ee9 T\u01b0 h&agrave;ng tu\u1ea7n: <strong>MUA 1 T\u1eb6NG 1<\/strong>&nbsp;cho b\u1ed9 s\u01b0u t\u1eadp Cocktails Dark &amp; Stormy, Cuba Libre, White Lady v&agrave; Tom Collins<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eebng n&ecirc;n b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 khung gi\u1edd v&agrave;ng <strong>Happy Hour<\/strong> t\u1eeb 17:00 \u0111\u1ebfn 19:00 c&aacute;c ng&agrave;y m\u1edf c\u1eeda v\u1edbi \u01b0u \u0111&atilde;i gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ebfn 50% gi&aacute; th&ocirc;ng th\u01b0\u1eddng d&agrave;nh cho c&aacute;c th\u1ee9c u\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ef1c \u0111\u01a1n ch\u1ecdn l\u1ecdc!<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">____________________<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u1ebft n&oacute;i, h\u1eb3n ch&uacute;ng s\u1ebd k\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t c&acirc;u chuy\u1ec7n d&agrave;i v\u1ec1 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ea7y m&agrave;u s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a Saigon Saigon Rooftop Bar, m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 &iacute;t qu&aacute;n bar c&ograve;n gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n&eacute;t \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng nguy&ecirc;n thu\u1ef7 trong nh\u1ecbp ph&aacute;t tri\u1ec3n nhanh ch&oacute;ng c\u1ee7a th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c&oacute; &ldquo;kh&aacute;i ni\u1ec7m&rdquo; v\u1ec1 qu&aacute;n bar tr&ecirc;n cao, bia th\u1ee7 c&ocirc;ng v&agrave; m\u1ea1ng x&atilde; h\u1ed9i, Saigon Saigon Rooftop Bar lu&ocirc;n l&agrave; n\u01a1i b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed3 u\u1ed1ng ngay t\u1eeb gi&acirc;y ph&uacute;t \u0111\u1ea7u ti&ecirc;n kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n m\u1edf c\u1eeda n\u0103m 1959. Th\u1eadm ch&iacute;, kh&ocirc;ng m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn n&agrave;o c&oacute; th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c&aacute;c ch&iacute;nh tr\u1ecb gia, nh&agrave; b&aacute;o v&agrave; binh s\u0129 \u0111ang kh&aacute;t, m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m tranh th\u1ee7 th\u1eddi gian th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c bia trong gi\u1edd \u01b0u \u0111&atilde;i b&ecirc;n kho\u1ea3ng s&acirc;n v&agrave; ban c&ocirc;ng nh&igrave;n ra th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1, d\u1ecdc theo m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng tuy\u1ebfn ph\u1ed1 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v&agrave; mang \u0111\u1eadm d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Ng&agrave;y nay, d&ugrave; nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 \u0111&atilde; thay \u0111\u1ed5i, tuy nhi&ecirc;n, v\u1eabn c&ograve;n \u0111&oacute; m\u1ed9t Saigon Saigon Rooftop Bar kh&ocirc;ng \u0111\u1ed5i thay v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, c&ugrave;ng v\u1ecb th\u1ebf \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong tr&aacute;i tim th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1, n\u01a1i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v&agrave; hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i lu&ocirc;n \u0111an xen v&agrave; song h&agrave;nh.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Saigon Saigon Rooftop Bar mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho du kh&aacute;ch th\u1ef1c \u0111\u01a1n m\u1edbi th&uacute; v\u1ecb, m\u1ed9t tho&aacute;ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb \u1ea9m th\u1ef1c Vi\u1ec7t Nam v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng m&oacute;n \u0111\u1ed3 nh\u1eafm v\u1eeba quen thu\u1ed9c l\u1ea1i ph&aacute; c&aacute;ch...c&ugrave;ng m\u1ed9t khung c\u1ea3nh tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi!<\/p>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute;left: 342px;top: 289.406px\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\">&nbsp;<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-48sutie2 buttons-el-wrapper text-center    fg-text-dark\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/SSRB-Master-Drink-List-0524.pdf\" class=\"ffb-block-button-1-0 ffb-btn ffb-btn-v1 ffb-btn-link  btn-base-brd-slide btn-slide  btn-base-md    btn-w-auto fg-text-dark ffb-button1-1\"><span class=\"btn-text\">XEM TH\u1ef0C \u0110\u01a0N<\/span><\/a><\/div><section class=\"ffb-id-82pqsp0e fg-section fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"fg-container container fg-container-large fg-container-lvl--2 \"><div class=\"fg-row row    \" ><div class=\"ffb-id-82pqsp0f fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-6 fg-text-dark\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-82pqsp0h fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/ssgb-3-1.jpg\" alt=\"ssgb-3\"><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-82pqsp0i fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-6 fg-text-dark\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-82pqsp0k fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/ssgb-2-1.jpg\" alt=\"ssgb-2\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><style>.ffb-id-48sutidr{ padding-top: 50px;padding-right: 50px;padding-bottom: 50px;padding-left: 50px;} .ffb-id-48sutids{ text-align: center;}.ffb-id-48sutidr .ffb-id-82pqsp0e{ padding-bottom: 20px;}@media (min-width:768px) { .ffb-id-48sutidr .ffb-id-82pqsp0e{ padding-bottom: 20px;}}@media (min-width:992px) { .ffb-id-48sutidr .ffb-id-82pqsp0e{ padding-bottom: 20px;}}@media (min-wi